The ete-maven-plugin facilitates the use of the library through a maven process.

The purpose of the whole project is to run an mda process.The core of the project is the ete-lib subproject.This project defines a process through pipelines of actions. Each action takes an eventual model on entry and returns a model.This diagram shows the very first layer : these packages enable embedding mda processes into a standard Java processEach package is materialized as a (sub)project
